Hello,

To crawl broadly you should change the first scope rule from RejectDecideRule to AcceptDecideRule. Then you may want to look through the rest of the scope and remove rules that no longer makes sense.

There is some information on hash mapped crawl config here: https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/Multiple+Machine+Crawling

Noah

